title: Maldives GDP From Manufacturing
description: GDP from Manufacturing in Maldives increased to 1527 MVR Million in 2021 from 1342 MVR Million in 2020. GDP from Manufacturing in Maldives averaged 1052.11 MVR Million from 1995 until 2021, reaching an all time high of 1680 MVR Million in 2019 and a record low of 488 MVR Million in 1996. This page provides - Maldives Gdp From Manufacturing- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Department of National Planning, Republic of Maldives
